{{Shortcut|QAT}}{{Stub/KO}}

QAT로 흔히 알려져있는 "Quality Assurance Team"은 적절하게 지명된 judicator들로서, 퀄리티를 조절하고 맵을 playability하게 만들기 위해 최근에 Qualified된 Beatmap들을 체크한다. retracting their qualified status as a disqualification notice where appropriate. They form the bulwark of standard control and enforce the basic expectation of quality for all beatmaps that enter the ranking process. 


QAT members will be held to strict activity standards as their role requires them to be regularly involved in assessing beatmap quality. 

Members of this team will be promoted from [[Beatmap_Nomination_Group|BN]], should they accept the new role offered.
Members of QAT have a red name in ingame chat and on the forums, whereas BN no longer do.

